{"tid":2301344,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"aespa的MV抄襲爭議，被抄襲藝術家回應：已經溝通過了！網友：「SM每次都出現爭議才要匯款嗎」","createTime":"2020-11-26T08:44:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-26T13:18:44.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"37c6080e79f12a925ed0ebf0d07391e0b4d85035","tid":2301344,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T08:44:20.000Z","msg":"SM新女團「aespa」日前帶著出道曲《Black Mamba》正式出道，但MV也引發了抄襲爭議。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有網友質疑《Black Mamba》MV許多場景會讓人聯想到《英雄聯盟》虛擬女團K/DA的《POP/STARS》。還有德國視覺藝術家Vacades（Timo Helgert）也通過IG限時動態發文：「我收到很多訊息，他們沒有經過我的同意，我們也沒有合作，看上去像是抄襲了（地鐵、蛇這兩個場景）。」（相關新聞：【韓網熱議】SM新女團「aespa」出道曲《Black Mamba》MV預告公開，被指出抄襲虛擬女團K/DA）<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_d8f5ce6416a805717798c0d39dc70310/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-26/131916-886447.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_d8f5ce6416a805717798c0d39dc70310%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-26%2F131916-886447.jpg&h=c96505c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_ae0057e61ae74da49ac9f13387f1a9b8/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-26/131916-886448.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_ae0057e61ae74da49ac9f13387f1a9b8%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-26%2F131916-886448.jpg&h=2f3a45c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日，德國視覺藝術家Vacades也在IG限時動態發文：「各位KPOP粉絲，我想把這件事說出來，澄清最近很多網站都在進行討論，我和aespa的MV導演已經溝通過了，雙方都能理解對方的創作過程，今後會支持這些女孩的，真心祝賀她們出道。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_91a72a047828e8bf8d855b8f4b6d170f/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-26/131916-886449.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_91a72a047828e8bf8d855b8f4b6d170f%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-26%2F131916-886449.png&h=94583e28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這也再次在韓網引發熱烈討論，網友：「先打包後結算～SM一直堅持的方式」、「哇！有點驚訝，原來是解決啊」、「所以K/DA呢」、「SM每次都出現抄襲爭議才匯款嗎」、「如果原作者什麼都不做會怎樣呢」、「真的先付費再用吧」、「這種事也不是一次兩次了，真的很可笑」、「有名的公司以這種方式進行後續結算」等等。<br />\n<br />\n另外，《Black Mamba》MV目前已有5500萬多的觀看人次，近日她們也在各音樂節目進行打歌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_325dd1d88f4a70f6374283a645ae3c02/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-26/131916-886450.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_325dd1d88f4a70f6374283a645ae3c02%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-26%2F131916-886450.jpg&h=bfdb0ff7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac16678fe892b5f8a5db3722d45f6321dd959023","tid":2301344,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T08:46:24.000Z","msg":"完蛋了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdd178bc793b724aa17809930c60407127c0460a","tid":2301344,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ac16678fe892b5f8a5db3722d45f6321dd959023","tid":2301344,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T08:46:24.000Z","msg":"完蛋了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T08:47:58.000Z","msg":"抵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd688a06159d35fc1fcd96eba93aea2335c201bc","tid":2301344,"uid":256952,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T12:02:44.000Z","msg":"抄你係睇得起你 屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a26cbe96806d74f160f10d74b2324cd4eb8f8e8e","tid":2301344,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"fd688a06159d35fc1fcd96eba93aea2335c201bc","tid":2301344,"uid":256952,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T12:02:44.000Z","msg":"抄你係睇得起你 屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T12:05:18.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkg